According to https://nodejs.org/api/timers.html#timers_settimeout_callback_delay_args, you can pass a value as well: `setTimeoutPromise(40, "foobar")`, so you might want to consider:
```ts
declare namespace setTimeout {
  export function __promisify__(ms: number): Promise<void>;
  export function __promisify__<T>(ms: number, value: T): Promise<T>;
}
```

